Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Have you heard the gossip already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Two shockingly beautiful glazzies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,A shockingly overflowing romance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,The hottest topic now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,It's all about this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,A charming lady from the Taishou Era
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,60,,How are you feeling? I'm Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me a High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,60,,to give me once again this loving glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is for me \Nto have this unrequited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,60,,How are you feeling? I'm Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,60,,Just a smidgen bit pretentious tomboyish lady
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(674.595,486.667)\blur0.667\bord0}\h Translation    alucardnoyuuutsu\h\N\h       Timing    Perevodildo         \h\NQC    Ziusudra\h
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady got woken up bright and early to learn housework the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a true High Collar Lady doesn't give up this easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we mustn't forget that she got all 1s for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're left with two guys who have been left alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and a boy that can't stand to lose-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, I meant a lady, High Collar Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This story takes place in London-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,err, wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we're at Ijuuins' mansion in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:53.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,300)\c&HFDEBE5&\pos(467.027,80)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60\b1}Episode 9\NThe first palpitation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know it, by Satsuma traditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,women eat alone in a corner in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, today you'll be eating in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really, Mrs. Kisaragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Then, Lady Benio, this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit here, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm awful at manners,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but having a nice meal in the morning doesn't sound bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chefs here must be skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you can bring breakfast at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nay,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't eat just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be teaching you politesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Politesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds delicious, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you need to behave
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not a dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know table manners before eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon appetit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so distracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me all the basic manners I've taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, cutlery must be used going from the most external pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Red wine must accompany meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,while white wine goes with fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, eating soup must be done silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, even prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,eat three meals a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did my breakfast go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiter, bring Lady Benio's breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they prepared for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,my mouth is watering!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One slice of bread? Just this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, eating too much is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, then let's dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you guess? To school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to this place, school is way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I really want to go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll be going, Mrs. Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait a minute, Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,do you not want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have the right to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go at all costs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Any issue with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you need to know that it's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw-aw-aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I wanted to teach you politesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?{I still can't understand what she means by 男遅れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The five fundamental seasonings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugar, salt, vinegar, soy sauce and miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that hard, you just need the spirit.{Dunno, she says something like [てき?]がその気ならこっちも[??]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The chef is here to explain how to\Nbake bread in a stove, please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A stove, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all you need to mix flour, yeast, a pinch of salt and butter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then you wait until it's fully risen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,after that the butter must be spread on the bottom of the baking tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you'd learn how to bake bread in a stove,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say I'd teach you how to prepare bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, just remember how to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,bake biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is flower arrangement{/ikebana}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just follow your instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This should give it a nice touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This should give it a nice touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's identical to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been attending some classes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at the prestigious Ikenobou school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is not Ikenobou style at all, it's just pathetic!{I wanted to keep the 池坊-でくの坊 joke but I couldn't find any good substitutes}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In our upper class society, fellowships,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,namely, social life, are the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll explain you how to knot-tie a mizuhiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,an envelope that's typically gifted during ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you listen, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'll be showing you how to knot-tie the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You put this like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,after that you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You bend that thing there, then you keep going that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn, Lady Benio, do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could try, but I've only seen it once...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll do it, .
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I bend this here, then I do it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Only hitting someone's weak points is so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, the early bird gets the worm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll learn all of the noble words and shock her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Omawari, akaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iriiri, okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{It's a cheatsheet with "noble" names for foods compared to how she is used to calling it: http://yctyct.blog64.fc2.com/blog-entry-706.html?sp - it's the same list as on 10:12 in ep2, so I borrowed partly modified alu's translation from there}{\bord6.667}Omawari = vegetables \NAkaka = red beans \NIriiri = roasted soybeans\N Okabe = tofu\N Misomiso = salad dressed with miso\N Harihari = dried melon\N Surusuru = dried squid{this part is omitted in ep2 and is hidden under the paper here so I made this up}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to remember even those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see this worn-out visage of yours, my chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to make a mess of this old-fashioned, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,static mansion that's binded by traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, High Collar Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is beating so deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta my way, go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, you're looking pretty pale lately, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been through a lot, but I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, couldn't you wake up a tad earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It can-t be helped,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to wake up early to learn chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and many times I stay up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,see you later, Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope I don't snag it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop- ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, hang in there, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm not my usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry up we won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ushigorou,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then, I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day and take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Benio, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? Your mission to destroy your engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great!\NDo your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand me the homework I assigned you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So shamelessly honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the housework I have to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,going to school is just a child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Benio, I know it's tough, but cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Boss, whenever I meet your father and Nanny,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,they always ask me about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never know how to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you deliver a letter to Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't understand these two lines as I don't get if he's talking about something positively or negatively}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a letter from Boss Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Give me the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, I'll deliver it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Great God {大明神 is translated as "deity with extraordinary spiritual powers" so something like this could fit - Alucard}{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/My%C5%8Djin - no clue what this sign hangs for here - perevodildo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hanamura, please read it as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll omit all of the introduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write this in one go.{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been spending my days at the Ijuuins' mansion safely,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all of the Ijuuins are deeply tender people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in particular, the count is incredibly kind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I deeply respect him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to all of them,\Nthere is nothing I have to worry about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sleep like a log and when I get up everything's clean and tidy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for kitchen chores, they didn't make me do anything at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moreover, I cheerfully enjoy my meals with the entire family,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so please don't worry about anything.\NYours truly, Benio.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,reading this relieved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delighted to read that she's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If Benio is speaking that fondly of her new life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it might be hard for her to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ushigorou,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... feel bad for Boss. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,are you saying that she's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading those contented words by Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,made me cry tears of joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it? Great, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Calligraphers have existed for a long time.{not too sure if this is the exact meaning}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that by reading those words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,Poems: Ancient and Modern{/Collection of Poems of Ancient and Modern Times}{古今集}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you can understand the writer's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is often only accredited to Fujiwara no Yukinari, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see you're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,diligently taking notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The three main calligraphers are Fujiwara no Yukinari,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara no Sukemasa and Ono no Toufuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Benio, will be learning about these three--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah-ah, that-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A character face!{へのへのもへじ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You didn't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the hinderance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to take Lady Benio's laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to do your laundry by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, Young Master's too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And Count's too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the duty of wives in the Ijuuin family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could die before Mrs. Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will be first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, what do you think about Young Master's fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I expected Young Master's wife to be as beautiful as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also pug-nosed, she'll just ruin his reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'd be better than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,True, true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm here because I wanted to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always trying to act young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you so incautious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing women's laundry on top of men's is an aberration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Men's laundry is going to be stained!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw this dirty laundry away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,such chauvinism, such anachronism,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sick of all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let that be a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,L-L-Lord, are you feeling alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you disrespect me that blatantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reluctant 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to go away because of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can't be helped,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if you talk that way about women,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... she's serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if women are as inferior as you think they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too impudent for a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you don't hold your life dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that I'll fall behind just like a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio and Lord are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it already begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too relaxed! Please, come stop Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Lord has aged,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but he has mastered martial arts in the Houzouin-ryuu school...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate L-Lady Benio is going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who's really in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, hurry up and stop your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just watch and you'll see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,my future wife's capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you even told me that you didn't mind if I messed your house up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep remembering it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The way my heart beat that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to run away halfway,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but at this stage I'll just take it as it comes, I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An elderly, yet still skillful warrior from Satsuma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,versus a girl from the Taishou era who's fighting for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One more stubborn than the other,\NGod only knows the outcome of this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They say not to pick up fights,{from now on I'm not too sure about all of this}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but seeing a tomboyish combat style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,knocking down an old count is great too!
